| Type   | Unit              | Variable Type | Description                                      | Sample Value       |
|--------|-------------------|---------------|--------------------------------------------------|--------------------|
| Input  | Clock             | Continuous    | Tracks current time continuously                 | 00:00              |
| Input  | Feed Time Schedule| Discrete      | Pre-set times for dispensing food                | 08:00, 18:00       |
| Input  | Food Level Sensor | Discrete      | Detects if food is available in the container    | Full, Low, Empty   |
| Output | Servo Motor       | Discrete      | Rotates to dispense food                         | Rotate 90Â°         |
| Output | Alert System      | Discrete      | Sends notification if issue occurs               | Food not eaten     |
